<span style="font-weight: bold;">Delivery</span><br>
Deliveries are from Mondays to Saturdays. We are closed on Public holidays.<br>
Spend more than $200 and get free delivery. If your order falls below $200, standard delivery is $15.<br>
<br>
<span style="font-weight: bold;">Failed Deliveries</span><br>
Rescheduling failed deliveries may incur additional fees. Reasons for a failed delivery include no recipients available to receive delivery or minors attempting to receive delivery.<br>
<br>
<span style="font-weight: bold;">Unavailable Items</span><br>
In the unlikely event that a requested item is out of stock, O&amp;B will notify you and recommend a substitute. If this is not to your liking, we will delivery the available items or cancel the order at your request.<br>All deliveries are subject to stock availability.<br>
<br>
<span style="font-weight: bold;">Upon Delivery</span><br>
Customers are requested to examine all goods upon delivery, any shortage or breakage must be brought to attention of the delivery personnel immediately and recorded on O&amp;B's delivery note.<br>
<br>
<span style="font-weight: bold;">Any other delivery questions</span><br>
For further assistance, please call 65341995 (9:00AM - 5:30PM Monday to Friday). You can also email us at <a href="mailto:contactus@oakandbarrel.com.sg">contactus@oakandbarrel.com.sg</a><br>
<br>
<span style="font-weight: bold;">Prices</span><br>
All prices on O&amp;B are in Singapore Dollars. There is no extra charge for GST.<br>
