<span style="font-weight: bold;">Electronic Tourist Refund Scheme by Global Tax Free</span><br>
The Electronic Tourist Refund Scheme (eTRS) enable foreign tourists to claim the Goods &amp; Services Tax (GST) that has been paid on their purchases electronically. O&amp;B will issue an eRTS ticket to the tourist at the point of purchase. If the purchases were made using cash, the eTRS tickets can still be used to apply for tax refund claims at the airport or cruise terminal.<br>
