<span style="font-weight: bold;">Returns and Complaints</span><br>
Your complete satisfaction is our absolute priority. Oak &amp; Barrel aims to provide quality products and service. If for any reasons you are dissatisfied with your purchase, kindly contact us within 7 days of received date at <span style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial;"><a href="mailto:contactus@oakandbarrel.com.sg">contactus@oakandbarrel.com.sg</a></span>. We enjoy receiving positive feedback!<br /><br /><br />
